{"tid":318200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認錯跑道] 加航客機幾乎撞四機 險釀史上最大空難","createTime":"2017-07-12T02:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T15:49:35.000Z","uid":34701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b623766ea52eed803a9841bc07db53daaeb5795b","tid":318200,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"加拿大航空一班客機的機師認錯跑道，上周五深夜飛抵美國三藩市國際機場時，幾乎降落在一條有四架客機等候的滑行道，險些釀成「史上最大空難」。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空管理局（FAA）表示，該架載着135名乘客和5名機員的A320空中巴士，獲准在「28右跑道」或「28R跑道」降落，但機師卻不慎試圖在「C滑行道」降落，空中交通管制員及時下令客機重飛，重新進入跑道並安全降落。<br />\n<br />\n控制塔要求客機改變航向時，C滑行道有四架客機等候起飛。聯合航空退休機長艾默爾（Ross Aimer）表示，如果客機真的降落在滑行道，很有可能釀成史上最嚴重空難。他說：「試想像一架空巴與四架載滿人和燃料的客機相撞，會有多可怕。」<br />\n<br />\n加航表示正調查該宗事件，暫時無資料補充。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳控制塔與加航機師的無線電通話。加航機師接到控制塔指示，在「28右跑道」降落。三藩市國際機場的「28右跑道」和「28左跑道」是平行的，「C滑行道」亦與「28右跑道」平行。<br />\n<br />\n機師接到指示後，發覺有問題，問控制塔：「這是加航759號班機，想確定一下，我見到跑道有燈光，肯定可以降落嗎？」控制塔回答說：「加航759號班機可以降落在28右跑道，跑道上別無他機。」機師說「OK」後，相信是地面一架等候起飛客機的機師突然插嘴問：「這人想去哪？他飛進了滑行道。」控制塔立即叫加航機師不要降落，立即重飛，機師遵照了指示。<br />\n<br />\n地面一架聯航客機的機師告訴控制塔：「加航客機在我們頭頂飛過。」控制塔答道：「無錯，我都見到。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499808986_414d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170712%2Flarge%2F1499808986_414d.jpg&h=712c4632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944255&d=tVQayoMpeeFv0KaNZAnvlkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=31a50517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944255&h=2f432e71\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944255</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da70e7c7bb69f6d82c4969a2e1fb1144b98bb51","tid":318200,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"認錯runway=/=認錯taxiway <br />\nTenerife Disaster 升4級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105faf3b472cf0645798c1358803944c0de4e2d3","tid":318200,"uid":122997,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"連登飛機達人點睇呢單野,重痴線過赤臘角東航120度幾乎撞山"},{"pid":"d7978e45cbf1e45df7e872439f0ba8b6e15daf28","tid":318200,"uid":34701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登飛機達人點睇呢單野,重痴線過赤臘角東航120度幾乎撞山</blockquote><br />\n我覺得真係出事嘅話炸咗個機場都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n模擬片段要搵Michael Bay拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c719c5fc01461f1e372b6dc2fb22333fc87a2c91","tid":318200,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"有時講錯同GET錯一句真係死好多人"},{"pid":"a9ab7a16e79c2d3b011fa6dc83a42088a70eb726","tid":318200,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"如果當時能見度低..."},{"pid":"2b11d00de0473867a00c6320847e7a1793607551","tid":318200,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"367131ec7b7fe663aacbc98b104c5a71b1599749","tid":318200,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔知做乜, 睇張圖幻想撞落去都已經好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1a86f73d7e3f5c0db9f09c76d0963720cea1b7","tid":318200,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"乜唔係有ILS 個d 輔助咩？<br />\n咁都可以入錯線<br />\n<br />\n不過美國d機場跑道設計真係差<br />\n兩條parallel 可以係隔離<br />\n有d仲要十字交叉重疊<br />\n咁多地點解唔整3條隔遠d既parallel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bda40375f96a1b532e1f8987d87aefe1657f507","tid":318200,"uid":4006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"但機師卻不慎試圖在「C滑行道」降落<br />\n<br />\n機師接到指示後，發覺有問題，問控制塔：「這是加航759號班機，想確定一下，我見到跑道有燈光，肯定可以降落嗎？」控制塔回答說：「加航759號班機可以降落在28右跑道，跑道上別無他機。」<br />\n<br />\n即係機師入錯跑道定控制塔俾錯信號"},{"pid":"45896d44715b2be3827eacd952df08163143d520","tid":318200,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機師認錯都發現有唔妥<br />\n控制塔只係話佢知佢可以解落個條跑道<br />\n最後要地面機師插嘴控制塔先知道</blockquote><br />\n&quot;The controller was coordinating with another facility when a flight crew of another airliner taxiing on taxiway C queried ATC where AC-759 was going and stated it appeared the aircraft was lined up with taxiway C.&quot;"},{"pid":"dbf5849cf8303708113e6a6c013516f65918a5d4","tid":318200,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cd4f2d4dbfbad5b8c40454e9f9e97a2125d172","tid":318200,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"兩個機師都無睇機場資料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"3a6db2e43c0df5158f73ad3f38d65091ebc13d0a","tid":318200,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d00eeeb54540a7bd47b79f239778b857c4ffb3","tid":318200,"uid":26506,"like":2,"disl